name: SALE: 2013 Vortex Letterpress Calendar Flat
description:
(* THIS CALENDAR IS NOT READY TO HANG BUT FLAT)
EDITION: 125 
SIZE: 6x11
PACKAGING: cello sleeve
WALL ART: Each of the 7 panels doubles as 5x7 or 6x6 wall art
IMAGES: more at http://inkandwit.blogspot.com/2012/11/2013-inkwit-letterpress-calendar-vortex.html 

If you need a larger custom order or a wholesale order please email me at info [!at] inkandwit.com

FEATURES:
Cherry Blossom Lake, Sakura, Japan
Machu Pichhu, Peru
Joshua Tree, California
Govardhan Hill, India
Pyramids of Giza, Egypt
Northern Lights, Iceland

These prints look great in a grid of white or natural wood frames. You will end up with seven since the cover can also be framed. Simply use a sharp exacto knife and trim off the bottom to the size of your choice. You can do 6x6 or 5x7 as the calendar is 6x11.

This is a limited edition of 125 calendars printed by Rachael and Jake at Pistachio Press in Rochester, NY
